metadata.name: Undefeated Samurai #1
metadata.description:
⚡️ Powered by NFT-Inator

Undefeated Samurai is a multiplayer VR role-playing (RPG) game that combines the VR experience with NFT technology. Combining a mesmeric virtual-reality experience and innovative NFT technology brings remarkable benefits for collectors and gamers. Additionally, the Undefeated Samurai metaverse is where players can socialize with each other while trying to be the one that survives.
